                        "id": "17946562979960905",
                        "text": "Sharing this affordable omakase spot in Tokyo located right at Tsukiji \ud83e\udd79\ud83c\udf63\n\n\ud83d\udccdSushi Yamaharu Tsukiji \u5c71\u6cbb \u7bc9\u5730 \u9ba8\n\ud83c\udff9From the main street , enter this small alley , find the small wooden signage and climb the stairs , push open the door and walk all the way to 3rd floor and you will find this amazing Omakase place.\n\n\ud83d\udd17 This place only accept reservation which can be made online with Tablecheck / Tabelog.\n\ud83d\udd17 https://www.tablecheck.com/en/sushi-yamaharu/reserve/message\n\n\ud83d\udcb3\ud83d\udcb0Accept both Cash and Card.\n5500\u00a5 / per person / 15 course\n\nSushi Lover ! Don't miss out this place if you are visiting Tokyo !\ud83c\uddef\ud83c\uddf5\ud83d\udc40\n#tokyofood #japantrip #tokyosushi #Tokyo #tsukiji"
                    }
                }
